Car Barriers

  • Truly innovative shapes and uncompromising safety: these are the credentials of the new Qik barrier.
  • Soft edges, rounded corners, high performance and suitability for any type of installation environment.
  • Newly designed and technically advanced, Qik is the ideal solution for a totally safe access control of medium to high transit environments such as hotels, banks, shopping malls, as.
  • well as blocks of flats, companies and camp sites, which always require access control of car parking areas, to ensure their use to authorised people only.

Technical features of the product range

  • CE marking
  • Direct current motor with high performance in terms of speed and number of operations; alternating current motor suitable for all applications requiring lower performance and shorter life
  • Gear motor mounted at right angle with the barrier exit in order to avoid the use of a lever system and to leave more space available for the control unit
  • Simple to install, the system ensures a very easy access to the control unit
  • The 24 V versions with encoder allow slowdowns and speed control. Possibility of using batteries and great operating intermittency
  • The MD1 display module can be used for the diagnostics and enhanced control of panel adjustments, updatable by means of DMCS software (barrier QIK 80EH)
